column17:
Product Description

Roots Comb No.33A is a dressing comb designed for long straight hair. Unlike ordinary combs Roots combs are handcrafted from a single piece of material (cellulose acetate) hence these combs do not cause allergic reactions and create less stactic. Roots combs have soft rounded teeth that do not scratch the scalp but stimulate natural oils in the hair to nourish the hair follicles to encourage faster growth and healthier hair.
